headline: ConocoPhillips (COP) Enters 20-year LNG Purchase Pact with Sempra Infrastructure
summary: ConocoPhillips (NYSE:COP) is one of the best dividend stocks to buy. On August 21, oil and gas giant ConocoPhillips entered a two-decade agreement to buy 4 MTPA of LNG from Sempra Infrastructure’s Port Arthur LNG Phase 2 project in Texas.
